This is Perry Como's 25th RCA Victor album. Recorded in the United Kingdom (UK) and the United States (US), it shares most of its tracks with Perry's album, The Best of British. This album was made for US release only, as The Best of British was the one offered for sale in the UK and Canada. Side One[1] Side Two[1] + Also on The Best of British album.
